The more powerful ARGB comes in 16.8M colours and is motherboard SYNC with the MUSETEX dedicated ARGB control board pre-installed in the case. More color and fun can be to play with than normal RGB!

Brilliant Customizable Lighting - Addressable ARGB LEDs controlled with 3 methods. 1.Remote Control: MN6-B PC Case is equipped with a unique music panel, music sync; 2.LED Button Control: 19 lighting colors for LED button on the I/O panel; 3.Motherboard Control: Only when the 5V3PIN cable on the control board is connected to the motherboard can the ARGB light synchronization be realized. (Note: 12V 4PIN motherboard is not suitable for motherboard control, Button control is recommended.)
